  "body": "> Introduce two new restrictions retroactively from genesis:\r\n>\r\n> 1. Consider any transaction invalid, where the nonce exceeds or equals to `2^64-1`.\r\n> 2. The `CREATE` and `CREATE2` instructions to abort with an exceptional halt, where the account nonce is `2^64-1`.\r\n\r\nThis was accepted on [ACD120](https://github.com/ethereum/pm/blob/master/All%20Core%20Devs%20Meetings/Meeting%20120.md#limiting-account-nonce-eip-2681-vs-3338).",
